Title: Local check with expired cache is now stale
Class: fix
Compatible: compat
Component: checks
Date: 1626954055
Edition: cre
Knowledge: doc
Level: 1
Version: 2.0.0p10

A cached local check which cache is expired (more than the staleness threshold
(defaults to 150%)) is now marked as stale. Before the latest cached result was
shown as if it was reported recently.
